---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: false
description: "SYNTHERION is a synthwave bullet-hell shooter where every weapon is a loop and every run is a song. Built in Godot."
---

{% include "partials/hero.njk" %}

<main>

<section id="pitch" class="section section--pitch">
  <p class="pitch">
    A Tyrian-style vertical shooter where <em>every weapon is an audio loop</em>.
    Fire on the grid, layer the sound, and your run becomes a track.
  </p>
  <ul class="features">
    <li>
      <h3>Beat-Synced Weapons</h3>
      <p>Each gun fires on a beat division. Stack loadouts to compose your own synthwave arrangement mid-fight.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Roguelike Runs</h3>
      <p>Procedural sectors, permadeath, meta-progression. Every attempt a new B-side.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Co-op (Planned)</h3>
      <p>Two-player couch and online. Duets in enemy airspace.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Original Soundtrack</h3>
      <p>A full analog-flavored score by synth heads who grew up on Tyrian and Raptor.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="section section--shots">
  <h2 class="section__heading">Transmissions</h2>
  <div class="shots">
    <figure><img loading="lazy" src="/assets/shot1.jpg" alt="Gameplay screenshot 1"></figure>
    <figure><img loading="lazy" src="/assets/shot2.jpg" alt="Gameplay screenshot 2"></figure>
    <figure><img loading="lazy" src="/assets/shot3.jpg" alt="Gameplay screenshot 3"></figure>
    <figure><img loading="lazy" src="/assets/shot4.jpg" alt="Gameplay screenshot 4"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--latest">
  <h2 class="section__heading">Latest Transmissions</h2>
  <div class="post-grid post-grid--latest">
    {% for post in collections.posts | limit(3) %}
      {% set post = post %}
      <div class="post-grid__item">
        {% include "partials/post-card.njk" %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="section__more">
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/devlog/">→ All transmissions</a>
  </div>
</section>
{# Watch trailer modal — added in Task 12 #}
<section class="section section--callout">
  <div class="callout-grid">
    <div class="callout">
      {% include "partials/buttondown.njk" %}
    </div>
    <div class="callout callout--discord">
      <h3 class="callout__title">Help shape the game</h3>
      <p class="callout__sub">Real input from players showing up early. Bug reports, feature requests, balance gripes — they all land.</p>
      <a class="btn btn--discord" href="{{ site.social.discordInvite }}" rel="noopener">Join the Discord →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</main>
